## CTA BUTTON (MANDATORY)

Every wizard step CTA MUST use this exact pattern:
```tsx
<div className="pt-6">
  <button
    onClick={next}
    disabled={!isValid}
    className="w-full h-14 rounded-2xl font-semibold text-base text-white shadow-md active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform flex items-center justify-center gap-2 disabled:opacity-40"
    style={{ background: isValid ? 'linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #10b981)' : '#9ca3af' }}
  >
    Fortsæt
    <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4" />
  </button>
</div>
```

Rules:
- Height: `h-14` (56px — large touch target)
- Radius: `rounded-2xl`
- Color: teal gradient (`#0d9488\` → `#10b981`) when enabled, neutral (`#9ca3af`) when disabled
- Always `disabled:opacity-40\` not `disabled:hidden`
- Always show ArrowRight icon on continue buttons
- Use Check icon on final save buttons

