## INPUT CARDS

Option cards (radio-style selections) MUST use:
```tsx
<button
  onClick={() => setAnswer('yes')}
  className={\`w-full text-left rounded-2xl border-2 px-5 py-4 transition-all ${
    answer === 'yes'
      ? 'border-emerald-400 bg-emerald-50/60'
      : 'border-foreground/10 bg-white/50 hover:border-foreground/20'
  }`}
>
  <div className="font-semibold">Ja</div>
  <div className="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-0.5">Kort forklaring</div>
</button>
```

Number inputs MUST use:
```tsx
<Input
  type="number"
  inputMode="numeric"
  className="h-11 rounded-xl text-right text-lg font-semibold"
  placeholder="0"
/>
```

